        <Parent_String>fire protection systems [300072222], protection systems [300072219], systems by function [300242038], systems (equipment) [300008550], Object Groupings and Systems (hierarchy name) [300241489], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
